{"tid":1594141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自願係黨鐵搞快閃","createTime":"2019-09-25T11:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:07:06.000Z","uid":30991,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a233da5fde18b9056fc400ce3ab2589e6664a78","tid":1594141,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"小弟想係黨鐡車廂入邊搞個快閃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593643</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時間：後日：6:00-7:00 放工時間<br />\n地點： 轉車站 油塘 太子 九龍塘 紅磡 金鐘 <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n歌曲: <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原因： 比啲平時冇咁得閒係商場支持，但係又想唱下歌仔既手足出嚟表達自己既信念。同埋幫啲廢老淨化下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算出唔到去發夢都可以用把聲嚟支持下手足，比大家知道點都好！核爆都唔割！<br />\n<br />\n（時間可以就返大家）同埋由於係快閃 唔該大家唱完Be Water 去返目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30a97f6956c7a35474761468c9bce54947e0eff","tid":1594141,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1bd4b04066fbf4941aed4a3edb0a9af2f640aaaa","tid":1594141,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73ba1af0e541c3e06ad44f11eed226e82a94d8b","tid":1594141,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"好少答黨鐵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe56b04e7c226fd2d21cdc8f9f182a5894f2c6db","tid":1594141,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73ba1af0e541c3e06ad44f11eed226e82a94d8b","tid":1594141,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201